Invocation Name: bloomsburg guide
des: A guide to Bloomsburg , Pennsylvania; providing an overview and history of the city, as well as places to visit. This skill can help you get around town to see what is worth seeing, and where you can stop to relax or grab a bite to eat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
